steps.title: I am authenticated user accessing "SOAP" API

I pass a "applicationId = ngapi#1756 and userId = API and dataSet = patentFamily and searchQuery = patentTypes:&quot;Diagnostic&quot; and queryLanguage = ssql and returnFields = patentTypes and returnLimit = 10 and offset = 0 and expectedValues = expsearch_pf_210.xls" as parameter to "asyncExportAdvancedSearchResults" operation
I call poll async "1" times with interval "1" seconds with input "applicationId = ngapi#1756 and userId = API" I should get the response
check the requested file is found in the following path "expsearch_pf_210.xls"
I get a response with "Diagnostic, Analysis and Assay" in column "Patent Type"
I am authenticated user accessing "SOAP" API
